comment: /**  * Applies the message to {@link org.apache.hadoop.hbase.filter.Filter} to context.  */
code: /**  * Applies the message to {@link org.apache.hadoop.hbase.filter.Filter} to context.  */ @Override public void apply(CamelContext context, HBaseRow rowModel) {     if (ModelAwareFilter.class.isAssignableFrom(getFilter().getClass())) {         ((ModelAwareFilter<?>) getFilter()).apply(context, rowModel).     } }

comment: /**  * Wraps an existing {@link SkipFilter} filter into a {@link ModelAwareSkipFilter}.  */
code: /**  * Wraps an existing {@link SkipFilter} filter into a {@link ModelAwareSkipFilter}.  */ public static ModelAwareSkipFilter wrap(SkipFilter filter) {     return new ModelAwareSkipFilter(filter.getFilter()). }
